  {
    "id": "2041210202519957728",
    "text": "Brent-WTI spreads will remain wide. US SPR release will offset the majority of the inventory draws from US commercial crude storage.\n\nAccording to our estimate, US commercial crude storage will be ~435 million bbls by the end of June.\n\nUS oil inventories will be the last to draw. https://t.co/7ndKV0wbNS",
    "createdAt": "2026-04-06T17:43:30.000Z",
    "username": "HFI_Research",
    "displayName": "HFI Research",
    "url": "https://x.com/HFI_Research/status/2041210202519957728",
    "photoUrl": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFPV2zEaUAAQspu.jpg",
