  {
    "id": "2041202353181962307",
    "text": "Final crude estimate for April 2 week.\n\nIt looks like US crude exports are finally starting to ramp with imports falling. We should start to see sizable draws in US commercial crude storage starting next week. \n\nThe flow impact is starting to hit onshore inventories. The buffer for oil-on-water is gone now.\n\nPrepare for widespread global onshore oil inventory draws.",
    "createdAt": "2026-04-06T17:12:19.000Z",
    "username": "HFI_Research",
    "displayName": "HFI Research",
    "url": "https://x.com/HFI_Research/status/2041202353181962307",
    "photoUrl": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFPOtu3b0AAq9kv.png",
