    "rawScore": 20668,
    "score": 13434
  },
  {
    "id": "2041180362135818360",
    "text": "I don’t get the ceasefire talk. \n\nThey are still bombing each other. Israel just bombed the South Pars petrochemical plant, Iran just bombed Basra oilfield in Iraq. \n\nIn normal times, anything related to these two strikes would’ve sent oil higher. \n\n🤷‍♂️",
    "createdAt": "2026-04-06T15:44:56.000Z",
    "username": "HFI_Research",
